BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Pregnancy is a time when nutrition matters more than ever - you're building a human! This) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (guide provides trimester-by-trimester nutrition, safe exercise guidelines, supplement) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (information, and wellness tracking to support you and your baby through all 40 weeks.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (Note: Every pregnancy is unique. This guide provides general evidence-based information.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (Always follow your healthcare provider's specific recommendations.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
