12 0 obj
<< /Length 2816 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 1: Understanding Pregnancy Nutrition) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Caloric Needs by Trimester) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (- First trimester: No extra calories needed \(focus on quality\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (- Second trimester: +340 calories per day) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (- Third trimester: +450 calories per day) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.2 Td (These are averages - your provider will guide you based on starting weight.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 584.4 Td (Key Nutrients for Pregnancy) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 562.4 Td (Folate \(600mcg DFE daily\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 546.4 Td (Critical for neural tube development. Needed before and during early pregnancy.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 532.4 Td (- Sources: Leafy greens, legumes, fortified foods) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 518.4 Td (- Supplement: Prenatal vitamin with methylfolate preferred) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 500.4 Td (Iron \(27mg daily\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 484.4 Td (Blood volume increases 50% during pregnancy. Iron prevents anemia.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 470.4 Td (- Sources: Red meat, lentils, spinach, fortified cereals) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.4 Td (- Take with vitamin C for better absorption) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 438.4 Td (Calcium \(1000mg daily\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 422.4 Td (Builds baby's bones and teeth. If you don't consume enough, baby takes from your bones.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 408.4 Td (- Sources: Dairy, fortified plant milk, leafy greens, sardines) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 390.4 Td (DHA Omega-3 \(300mg daily\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 374.4 Td (Critical for baby's brain and eye development.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 360.4 Td (- Sources: Fatty fish \(2-3 servings/week\), DHA supplement) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 342.4 Td (Choline \(450mg daily\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 326.4 Td (Brain development and prevents neural tube defects. Often missing from prenatals.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 312.4 Td (- Sources: Eggs \(1 egg = 150mg\), liver, meat, fish) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 294.4 Td (Protein \(75-100g daily\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 278.4 Td (Builds baby's tissues, placenta, and supports blood volume.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 264.4 Td (- Sources: Meat, fish, eggs, dairy, legumes) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 234.6 Td (Foods to Avoid During Pregnancy) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 216.6 Td (- Raw or undercooked meat, fish, eggs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 202.6 Td (- High-mercury fish \(shark, swordfish, king mackerel, tilefish\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 188.6 Td (- Unpasteurized dairy and juice) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 174.6 Td (- Deli meats \(unless heated until steaming\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 160.6 Td (- Raw sprouts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 146.6 Td (- Alcohol \(no safe amount during pregnancy\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 132.6 Td (- Excessive caffeine \(limit to 200mg/day = 1 cup coffee\)) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
