BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 5: Exercise During Pregnancy) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Benefits of Prenatal Exercise) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (- Reduces risk of gestational diabetes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (- Helps manage healthy weight gain) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (- Reduces back pain and constipation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.2 Td (- May shorten labor and reduce c-section risk) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.2 Td (- Improves mood and sleep) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 586.2 Td (- Faster postpartum recovery) Tj ET
