BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Depends on starting BMI: Normal weight: 25-35 lbs, Overweight: 15-25 lbs, Underweight:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (28-40 lbs, Obese: 11-20 lbs. Your provider will give personalized guidance.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 618.4 Td (Q: Is caffeine safe?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (Up to 200mg/day \(about one 12oz coffee\) is considered safe. Some providers recommend less.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (Avoid energy drinks entirely.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 560.6 Td (Q: Can I eat sushi?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.6 Td (Raw fish carries infection risk during pregnancy. Cooked sushi rolls \(shrimp tempura,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (California roll with imitation crab\) are fine. Low-mercury cooked fish is encouraged.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 502.8 Td (Q: What about food cravings?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.8 Td (Cravings are normal and okay to indulge in moderation. If craving non-food items \(ice,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (dirt, chalk\) - this is called pica and may indicate a nutritional deficiency. Tell your) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 458.8 Td (provider.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 431.0 Td (Q: Do I really need a prenatal vitamin?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 415.0 Td (Yes. It's very difficult to get adequate folate, iron, and DHA from food alone during) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 401.0 Td (pregnancy. Think of it as insurance for any nutritional gaps.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 373.2 Td (Q: Is exercise safe in the third trimester?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 357.2 Td (Yes, unless your provider says otherwise. Modify as needed - reduce intensity, avoid) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 343.2 Td (overheating, stop if anything feels wrong. Walking and swimming are excellent throughout.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 315.4 Td (Q: What if I can't keep anything down?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 299.4 Td (Severe nausea/vomiting \(hyperemesis gravidarum\) affects 1-3% of pregnancies and needs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 285.4 Td (medical treatment. If you cannot keep food/water down for 24 hours, contact your provider.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 257.6 Td (Q: Can I diet during pregnancy?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 241.6 Td (Pregnancy is not the time for weight loss diets. Focus on nutrient quality, not) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 227.6 Td (restriction. If overweight, your provider may recommend modest calorie awareness without) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 213.6 Td (restriction.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
